{"tid":1358532,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"本人正式發起港鐵跨欄運動！","createTime":"2019-07-24T02:57:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T05:52:57.000Z","uid":251052,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"d8342a306a6eb715c8b0c183da78e1cf8f31149f","tid":1358532,"uid":251052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T02:57:24.000Z","msg":"近日，港鐵沙田站及元朗站發生多宗恐怖襲擊事件，而港鐵方面未有及時協助乘客或市民不特止，更加有協助恐怖份子既嫌疑！<br />\n<br />\n所以，本人正式發起港鐵跨欄(跳閘)運動，同時支持其他所有不合作運動。"},{"pid":"0a52214cd2267ab27342e9ea3ab10bb3afaddc8a","tid":1358532,"uid":165246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T02:58:35.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">請大家一定要記得！！！！<br />\n１。全面撤回逃犯條例<br />\n２。撤銷暴動定性<br />\n３。釋放被捕義士並承諾永不追究<br />\n４。全面實行雙普選<br />\n５。成立獨立調查委員會追究黑警責任＋徹查警黑勾結元朗站暴打站內市民<br />\n6 。721上環對示威者開36槍 義士被狗開槍擊中 下落不明<br />\n要求公佈義士下落<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n光復香港 時代革命<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"bebe3ee22c977f4e1da8f37bc6f1e7da45021ffc","tid":1358532,"uid":251052,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T02:59:47.000Z","msg":"但跨欄同阻擋車門關閉唔同，有一定風險，參與者有量力而為。<br />\n唔想跨欄既亦可以使用特惠票。"},{"pid":"f6365de209b576b5ae09d9b914c08f97f71f4470","tid":1358532,"uid":11804,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T02:59:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d89d37a683e13a34c6a913ea1f8dad1ce55c91b5","tid":1358532,"uid":251052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f6365de209b576b5ae09d9b914c08f97f71f4470","tid":1358532,"uid":11804,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"d8342a306a6eb715c8b0c183da78e1cf8f31149f","tid":1358532,"uid":251052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1